  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dive into the hand-drawn Metroidvania world of <i>Super Roboy</i>!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle mutants and machines while exploring an interconnected map and learning enemies’ skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756020/extras/c51608d4432fd54ed28b45b223d663bf.poster.avif?t=1765786165\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756020/extras/c51608d4432fd54ed28b45b223d663bf.webm?t=1765786165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756020/extras/c51608d4432fd54ed28b45b223d663bf.mp4?t=1765786165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• <strong>Learn enemy skills</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat enemies to acquire a wide variety of skills, including movement upgrades and powerful new weapons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756020/extras/6ba50afe4c7e2475d64f114afc988ce7.poster.avif?t=1765786165\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756020/extras/6ba50afe4c7e2475d64f114afc988ce7.webm?t=1765786165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756020/extras/6ba50afe4c7e2475d64f114afc988ce7.mp4?t=1765786165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• <strong>Face off against hand-drawn bosses</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge a variety of uniquely designed, hand-drawn bosses that test your skills and bring the world of <i>Super Roboy</i> to life with striking visual flair.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756020/extras/53c8cd69de6a7b3bf2ddff22332d4a1e.poster.avif?t=1765786165\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756020/extras/53c8cd69de6a7b3bf2ddff22332d4a1e.webm?t=1765786165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756020/extras/53c8cd69de6a7b3bf2ddff22332d4a1e.mp4?t=1765786165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• <strong>Explore</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Freely explore a richly detailed sci-fi, post-apocalyptic world. Stray from the main path to discover hidden rewards</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756020/extras/48289d4a1b1757a7402c67388e28d21b.poster.avif?t=1765786165\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756020/extras/48289d4a1b1757a7402c67388e28d21b.webm?t=1765786165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756020/extras/48289d4a1b1757a7402c67388e28d21b.mp4?t=1765786165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• <strong>Uncover Roboy’s past</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a touching story inspired by <i>Dante’s Divine Comedy</i> and classic sci-fi novels, brought to life through comic-style cutscenes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756020/extras/a1502efb6c203898929d394e74222875.poster.avif?t=1765786165\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756020/extras/a1502efb6c203898929d394e74222875.webm?t=1765786165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756020/extras/a1502efb6c203898929d394e74222875.mp4?t=1765786165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• <strong>Exploit enemy weaknesses</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master elements, inflict status effects, and learn unique attacks to deal devastating blows to tough opponents.</p>",
